[{"client_msg_id":"2a9e2bd4-19a8-4778-90b4-71bdd745fde8","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"Vim script の名前空間の話、やっぱり autoload を使うのはおかしい。\n例えばスクリプトの中に名前空間を絶対で表記するとその名前空間に固定されてしまうので、\nディレクトリを変えると当然名前が名前空間に合ってないとエラーになる。\n理想は、スクリプト中では相対表記で書いて、import する側（ライブラリのユーザ側）が配置を自由に選べるといい。","ts":"1577893383.179200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"k/p"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"1ac2c53d-9849-4e34-852e-e23ff1950ff8","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"たとえば callbag.vim\n<https://github.com/vim-jp/vital.vim/issues/623#issuecomment-569984038|https://github.com/vim-jp/vital.vim/issues/623#issuecomment-569984038>\nの callbag# って名前空間を、プラグインリポジトリ内でのスクリプトの配置を変えることによって myplugin#callbag# みたいに変えられてほしい。","ts":"1577893402.179300","attachments":[{"fallback":"GitHub: add support for CancellationTokenSource and CancellationToken · Issue #623 · vim-jp/vital.vim","id":1,"title":"add support for CancellationTokenSource and CancellationToken · Issue #623 · vim-jp/vital.vim","title_link":"https://github.com/vim-jp/vital.vim/issues/623#issuecomment-569984038","text":"CancellationTokenSource examples: <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dotnet/standard/threading/cancellation-in-managed-threads> <https://github.com/axios/axios> Abort Controllers: <https://developer.mozi>...","thumb_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/1051958?s=400&v=4","blocks":null,"service_name":"GitHub","service_icon":"https://a.slack-edge.com/80588/img/unfurl_icons/github.png","thumb_width":400,"thumb_height":400,"from_url":"https://github.com/vim-jp/vital.vim/issues/623#issuecomment-569984038","original_url":"https://github.com/vim-jp/vital.vim/issues/623#issuecomment-569984038"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"c46"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"c76a0ac4-d07d-44d6-9de8-4d15fee783df","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"逆に衝突安全のために、(安全な)絶対名があるところまではよくて、pythonのimportみたいに、別名というか短縮名で利用できる、もアリなのかもしれないが...実例がないとどっちがいいかは難しいかな...","ts":"1577929060.181200","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"voI"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"fecc6430-cec8-481b-bc24-e4dc5282455a","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"すみません、↑のやつ昨日風呂入ったら別にそんなことはないな…って思ってからコメントするの忘れてました…","ts":"1577929471.182500","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"LJD"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"c8445c97-7d3d-4cbe-98d3-ebec490aa27e","type":"message","user":"U0M7GCBPD","text":"node.js とかでも node_modules (=rtp) のものは npm のモジュール名 (=絶対表記) で指定するし、わざわざコピーして持ってくるケースがレアケースなんですよね","ts":"1577929562.184000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"vIjo"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"7f66a1e7-5783-4e54-8786-ef11ec95d66f","type":"message","user":"UAZ33BKV2","text":"なるほど","ts":"1577929620.185000","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"vUMk"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"8106cb09-50ff-452c-8c3e-d3032679e0ff","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"autuload がディレクトリ別れてても実行時にはバッティングしうるって所が罠なんですよね。","ts":"1577931700.186800","team":"T03C4RC8V","reactions":[{"name":"sorena","count":2,"users":["UAZ33BKV2","U0M7GCBPD"]}],"replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"wah"}],"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"}]
